7. For those that haven't been paying attention, there are at least 2 large Asian guilds on the server now, both with multiple players lvl 50+.  Neither posts here, I seriously doubt either will check the calendar before they raid.<br>
8. For all practical purposes the server has gone FFA and all the bitching to the contrary isn't going to change it.<br>
